==诊断==
咖啡牛奶斑的诊断主要靠视诊，测量色斑的大小和数量，对诊断相关的疾病如Ⅰ型神经纤维瘤病具有重要意义。

==治疗==
咖啡牛奶斑可以使用[[激光|激光]]治疗<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://emedicine.medscape.com/article/1120359-overview |title="Laser Treatment of Benign Pigmented Lesions", by Noah S Scheinfeld, MD, JD, FAAD |accessdate=2011-12-02 |archive-date=2019-08-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190810114717/https://emedicine.medscape.com/article/1120359-overview |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==预后==
咖啡牛奶斑是良性疾病，本身不会造成任何损害。

